room_title: Escape room "Nefertari's Tomb" by NM Escape Room in Albuquerque
room_address: 4401 McLeod Rd Suite B Albuquerque, NM 87109
room_description: You are tomb robbers serving a criminal organization in search of the real tomb of Nefertari. Armed with a list of artifacts, you must dynamite your way into the tomb, steal as many valuables as you can and escape before the authorities arrive. That's not all: once the mission is finished, you must blow up the tomb to bury your tracks and make your escape.
